title: iGym 247 Australia
description:
With the iGym 247 App, you are now able to optimise your time and maximise the convenience of signing up for classes from your device! Download today!

Browse, book or cancel class booking at any iGym location and add them automatically to your mobile device! 

See the weekly class schedules, browse and read up about new and exciting classes to the schedule before you attend. 

An App designed around your fitness needs. Not only will the iGym 247 App keep track of all of your class booking in the 'My Classes' section, It will also schedule and send you reminders on upcoming Personal Training sessions.

To set up a password and login, enter the email address registered to your iGym account and select 'forget password'. Alternatively contact your local club to help with this process or any other assistance.
